
<section id="MathAmp">
  <title>Amplitude Converters</title>

  <para>
    Opcodes to convert between different amplitude measurements are:
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="ampdb"><citetitle>ampdb</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="ampdbfs"><citetitle>ampdbfs</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="db"><citetitle>db</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="dbamp"><citetitle>dbamp</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem><para><link linkend="dbfsamp"><citetitle>dbfsamp</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    Use <link linkend="rms"><citetitle>rms</citetitle></link> to find the rms value of a signal. See also <link linkend="Zerodbfs"><citetitle>0dbfs</citetitle></link> for another way to handle amplitudes in csound.
  </para>

</section>
